name: Josefine
description:
Josefine is an ORIGINAL artwork painted in acrylic on canvas. The painting measures 24" x 30". It is inspired by a set of lyrics which I wrote, they go like this...

When Josefine sings her song
Well, you know that feeling
The one where you start to fall
Then just catch yourself

Well, it's just the same as that
Yeah but then it's over
And you realise
She wasn't singing at all.
